7
00:01:05,910 --> 00:01:07,040
The war ten years ago

8
00:01:07,270 --> 00:01:08,720
led to the closure of the market.

9
00:01:08,720 --> 00:01:11,130
People avoided this area due to superstitions.

10
00:01:11,130 --> 00:01:12,250
But it's still

11
