14
00:01:34,270 --> 00:01:35,400
Something is fishy.

15
00:01:41,870 --> 00:01:42,530
Be careful.

16
00:01:45,789 --> 00:01:46,789
So petty.

17
00:01:49,640 --> 00:01:50,479
You too.

18
00:02:26,740 --> 00:02:29,400
-We've got to leave now.
-We've got to leave now.

19
00:02:29,400 --> 00:02:30,600
Let's get out of here.

20
00:02:37,030 --> 00:02:38,240
Why was there

21
00:02:38,560 --> 00:02:40,230
an altar like Fang Zhibo's

22
00:02:40,560 --> 00:02:41,680
with the Sea Chart?

23
00:02:42,090 --> 00:02:43,090
The Chart is fake.

24
00:02:43,670 --> 00:02:45,470
Someone is trying to lure us out.

25
00:02:47,970 --> 00:02:48,680
[Pingzhou]

26
00:02:51,160 --> 00:02:51,900
Xi'er.

27
00:02:53,320 --> 00:02:54,120
What's wrong?

28
00:02:59,310 --> 00:03:01,170
Things are getting interesting.

29
00:03:03,240 --> 00:03:04,640
Two Pingzhou cities.

30
00:03:20,760 --> 00:03:22,430
There are two Pingzhou cities.

31
00:03:22,430 --> 00:03:23,590
One is deserted,

32
00:03:23,880 --> 00:03:25,360
while the other is bustling with people.

33
00:03:25,360 --> 00:03:26,390
Murder!

34
00:03:26,440 --> 00:03:27,240
Help!

35
00:03:27,480 --> 00:03:30,090
Help! Someone fell into the water!

36
00:03:30,579 --> 00:03:31,150
Let's take a look.

37
00:03:31,150 --> 00:03:31,890
Help!

38
00:03:32,910 --> 00:03:33,750
Miss.

39
00:03:35,670 --> 00:03:37,340
Please save her.

40
00:03:38,079 --> 00:03:40,320
Miss, please save my Young Miss.

41
00:03:41,440 --> 00:03:43,670
Who is she?

42
00:03:43,900 --> 00:03:44,900
In my opinion,

43
00:03:45,030 --> 00:03:46,270
women should stay at home

44
00:03:46,270 --> 00:03:48,550
and practice music, chess, calligraphy, and painting.

45
00:03:48,550 --> 00:03:49,950
Look at your wife here,

46
00:03:50,110 --> 00:03:51,570
helping retrieve bodies.

47
00:03:51,770 --> 00:03:53,630
It's not good for her reputation.

48
00:03:53,750 --> 00:03:55,750
She's helping people.

49
00:03:56,320 --> 00:03:57,670
How come in this day and age,

50
00:03:57,670 --> 00:03:59,470
even saving lives can be shameful?

51
00:03:59,470 --> 00:04:00,590
If she were a man,

52
00:04:00,960 --> 00:04:02,620
you'd be singing her praises.

53
00:04:03,350 --> 00:04:04,950
But because she's a woman...

54
00:04:05,160 --> 00:04:06,350
For most people,

55
00:04:07,100 --> 00:04:08,360
that reason is enough.

56
00:04:09,690 --> 00:04:10,770
In this world,

57
00:04:11,080 --> 00:04:12,750
some people have it tough.

58
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:14,910
She made herself strong

59
00:04:14,910 --> 00:04:16,779
due to her past hardships.

60
00:04:17,370 --> 00:04:19,430
If it weren't for her past suffering,

61
00:04:19,829 --> 00:04:21,290
she wouldn't be like this.

62
00:04:21,880 --> 00:04:23,960
Talking like this now will only remind her of

63
00:04:23,960 --> 00:04:26,090
the discriminatory looks around her.

64
00:04:26,880 --> 00:04:27,520
Stop it.

65
00:04:38,100 --> 00:04:39,360
Sagebrush on the Snow.

66
00:04:39,920 --> 00:04:40,720
Miss.

67
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:42,040
Miss.

68
00:04:43,030 --> 00:04:44,750
It's all Yin Sanniang's fault.

69
00:04:44,750 --> 00:04:45,950
If it weren't for her,

70
00:04:46,000 --> 00:04:48,230
you wouldn't have died.

71
00:04:48,810 --> 00:04:50,340
What are you talking about?

72
00:04:51,310 --> 00:04:52,970
Yin Sanniang should be the one

73
00:04:53,040 --> 00:04:54,870
who got married to the Divine Man.

74
00:04:54,870 --> 00:04:56,310
But somehow,

75
00:04:56,330 --> 00:04:57,960
she suddenly disappeared.

76
00:04:58,270 --> 00:04:59,070
This morning,

77
00:04:59,170 --> 00:05:00,620
Sagebrush on the Snow

78
00:05:00,980 --> 00:05:03,490
appeared in my Young Miss's room.

79
00:05:04,130 --> 00:05:06,250
This is the symbol of betrothal.

80
00:05:09,320 --> 00:05:10,110
Gentlemen,

81
00:05:10,640 --> 00:05:11,920
you may not know,

82
00:05:12,390 --> 00:05:13,510
but Pingzhou

83
00:05:14,070 --> 00:05:16,550
has been plagued by strange occurrences since ten years ago.

84
00:05:16,550 --> 00:05:18,160
We frequently heard the hooting of owls.

85
00:05:18,160 --> 00:05:19,690
People who went out at night

86
00:05:19,840 --> 00:05:22,760
could even hear the sounds of carts and horses in the mountains.

87
00:05:22,760 --> 00:05:25,600
But when we sent people

88
00:05:25,760 --> 00:05:27,290
to investigate in broad daylight,

89
00:05:27,290 --> 00:05:28,890
we found nothing.

90
00:05:29,270 --> 00:05:30,800
Yes.

91
00:05:31,950 --> 00:05:35,580
Also, the old city often reeked of decay.

92
00:05:36,230 --> 00:05:39,340
So, residents moved to the outskirts,

93
00:05:39,830 --> 00:05:42,880
establishing another Pingzhou city.

94
00:05:43,640 --> 00:05:44,600
Did the government do nothing?

95
00:05:44,600 --> 00:05:46,270
Sir, in Pingzhou,

96
00:05:46,510 --> 00:05:49,370
the Divine Man is more trusted than the government.

97
00:05:49,420 --> 00:05:51,270
Even the relocation of the city five years ago

98
00:05:51,270 --> 00:05:52,730
was the order of the Divine Man.

99
00:05:52,730 --> 00:05:53,600
The Divine Man?

100
00:05:54,370 --> 00:05:56,760
He's the hero, Sagebrush on the Snow.

101
00:05:57,320 --> 00:05:58,320
Hero?

102
00:05:59,230 --> 00:06:00,040
In short,

103
00:06:00,110 --> 00:06:01,910
the Divine Man saved Pingzhou

104
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:03,430
and protected us.

105
00:06:03,640 --> 00:06:05,110
According to what you said,

106
00:06:05,110 --> 00:06:06,320
Sagebrush on the Snow

107
00:06:06,320 --> 00:06:07,920
should be a virtuous person.

108
00:06:08,670 --> 00:06:10,130
But why is he continuously

109
00:06:10,530 --> 00:06:11,950
marrying innocent girls?

110
00:06:11,950 --> 00:06:14,440
Since we've received divine blessings,

111
00:06:14,440 --> 00:06:16,240
we should pay reverence and offerings.

112
00:06:16,240 --> 00:06:17,970
I think you are a bunch of fools.

113
00:06:18,110 --> 00:06:19,830
You have no idea what you're doing.

114
00:06:19,830 --> 00:06:21,110
You don't even know

115
00:06:21,140 --> 00:06:22,400
who that Divine Man is.

116
00:06:24,870 --> 00:06:25,670
Let me ask you.

117
00:06:26,160 --> 00:06:27,290
Who is Yin Sanniang?

118
00:06:27,920 --> 00:06:30,780
You can go to the Flower Tower for more information.

119
00:06:31,230 --> 00:06:33,070
Everyone knows about it.

120
00:06:33,300 --> 00:06:34,480
Flower Tower?

121
00:06:41,990 --> 00:06:44,270
[Flower Tower]

122
00:06:45,430 --> 00:06:47,030
Isn't this...

123
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:49,390
Looks like Yun Shanjun

124
00:06:49,720 --> 00:06:51,120
has opened a branch here.

125
00:06:53,790 --> 00:06:56,720
Is it necessary to go this far just to keep an eye on us?

126
00:07:02,250 --> 00:07:03,050
You can't

127
00:07:04,930 --> 00:07:05,790
go in like this.

128
00:07:21,530 --> 00:07:22,530
What do you think?

129
00:07:23,230 --> 00:07:24,750
She's not very beautiful.

130
00:07:25,110 --> 00:07:26,510
The price won't be high.

131
00:07:28,990 --> 00:07:30,650
Since I'm here to sell my wife,

132
00:07:31,280 --> 00:07:33,409
you should know I urgently need money.

133
00:07:33,840 --> 00:07:35,230
It's not honest of you

134
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:37,100
to take advantage of me.

135
00:07:37,100 --> 00:07:38,700
You must be joking.

136
00:07:39,150 --> 00:07:41,120
Why not calm down a bit

137
00:07:41,850 --> 00:07:42,720
and we can

138
00:07:43,470 --> 00:07:44,720
negotiate.

139
00:07:52,230 --> 00:07:53,630
You made fun of me today.

140
00:07:55,340 --> 00:07:56,480
So, we're even now.

141
00:07:57,230 --> 00:07:58,480
You...

142
00:07:59,270 --> 00:08:00,230
Good acting.

143
00:08:01,760 --> 00:08:02,600
Surprised?

144
00:08:02,920 --> 00:08:04,360
We already saw this coming.

145
00:08:04,360 --> 00:08:05,430
There is no one

146
00:08:05,690 --> 00:08:06,690
in this brothel.

147
00:08:06,880 --> 00:08:08,840
You let us in so easily,

148
00:08:09,230 --> 00:08:11,630
along with the perfect timing of that maid.

149
00:08:11,960 --> 00:08:13,550
Do you really think we're fools?

150
00:08:13,550 --> 00:08:14,170
Tell me.

151
00:08:14,680 --> 00:08:15,940
Where is Yin Sanniang?

152
00:08:20,410 --> 00:08:22,070
What scheme are you planning?

153
00:08:22,110 --> 00:08:24,240
You want to know where Yin Sanniang is?

154
00:08:24,670 --> 00:08:25,550
Fine.

155
00:08:25,810 --> 00:08:28,000
But I'm afraid you won't live to find out.

156
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:30,160
She's just an unlicensed prostitute

157
00:08:30,160 --> 00:08:31,400
whose husband and child died long ago.

158
00:08:31,400 --> 00:08:33,340
She doesn't respect the Buddha at all.

159
00:08:33,340 --> 00:08:35,320
With her beauty, she stole my clients

160
00:08:35,320 --> 00:08:37,710
and hid in the fish market.

161
00:08:38,090 --> 00:08:40,620
Why are you making such a fuss looking for her?

162
00:08:41,280 --> 00:08:42,080
Good.

163
00:08:44,600 --> 00:08:45,410
Come in.

164
00:08:57,080 --> 00:08:59,640
Sir, come on.

165
00:08:59,670 --> 00:09:00,440
Come and play.

166
00:09:00,440 --> 00:09:01,500
What are you doing?

167
00:09:02,590 --> 00:09:03,200
No, no, no.

168
00:09:03,960 --> 00:09:04,430
Sir.

169
00:09:04,450 --> 00:09:05,520
What are you doing?

170
00:09:06,080 --> 00:09:07,350
Sir, don't be shy.

171
00:09:07,350 --> 00:09:08,110
Let go.

172
00:09:08,250 --> 00:09:08,730
You...

173
00:09:08,760 --> 00:09:10,030
Where are you touching? What are you doing?

174
00:09:10,030 --> 00:09:11,400
How inappropriate!

175
00:09:11,420 --> 00:09:13,130
No! Let go of me!

176
00:09:13,670 --> 00:09:14,430
[Sagebrush on the Snow]

177
00:09:13,880 --> 00:09:14,540
Let go of me!

178
00:09:14,540 --> 00:09:16,660
Sir, come on!

179
00:09:17,030 --> 00:09:18,160
-Move!
-Let go of me!

180
00:09:18,760 --> 00:09:19,230
Go away!

181
00:09:19,250 --> 00:09:19,970
Xi'er.

182
00:09:20,150 --> 00:09:21,590
Xi'er, come and help.

183
00:09:22,790 --> 00:09:24,200
Let me help you.

184
00:09:24,360 --> 00:09:25,470
-Sir.
-Don't move.

185
00:09:26,150 --> 00:09:26,910
Xi'er is missing.

186
00:09:26,910 --> 00:09:27,710
Sir.

187
00:09:28,000 --> 00:09:28,790
Xi'er.
